title: Deep Purple - Knock The Truckin.
description:
Deep Purple: Knock The Truckin' - Turin, Italy + Kassel, Germany '88

Recorded Live at (d1+d2) Stadio Comunale, Turin, Italy on September 21, 1988 
and (d3+d4) Eissporthalle, Kassel, Germany on September 24, 1988.

Excellent Soundboard Recording -> Bootleg Silver CD :: CBR 320 kbps.
